reviewText: The cover looked cute, the write up sounded cute, and I bought it to add to my Christmas collection.  The movie is not the greatest or the worse.  I may watch it again next year, and maybe not.
This movie was wonderful.  It kept the attention of my grandchildren.  They loved it.  I appreciate the service I received.

I have two little girls who love Christmas movies and will watch almost anything to do with Christmas. It kept my 4 year olds attention, but not my 2 year old. Quality is pretty poor and I honestly don't remember the storyline. Put it on for the kids when you need to get some stuff done...if it holds their attention.
The merchandise was sent in a timely manner and in excellent condition.  The CD played well and there was no damage, i.e., scratches etc.
